 will be a book that I will read many times and I will notice something slightly different. Even though I read the book with the attention that a predator gives its prey.</p> <p>This dystopian thriller had me gripped from the beginning. I think that this is a clever idea that has been perfectly executed - I can’t wait for the rest of the series!</p> <ul> <li><strong>Buy this book at the <a href=\"https://bookshop.theguardian.com/catalog/product/view/id/306435/\">Guardian Bookshop</a>.</strong><br /></li> </ul> <h2><strong>Want to tell the world about a book you’ve read? <a href=\"http://preview.gutools.co.uk/books/childrens-books/2011/mar/02/how-do-i-get-involved-guardian-childrens-books\">Join the site</a> and send us your review!</strong></h2>","productionOffice":"UK","hasStoryPackage":"false","trailText":"<strong>The Fanatical Reader: </strong>‘This dystopian thriller had me gripped from the beginning’","headline":"Red Queen by Victoria Aveyard – review","byline":"The Fanatical Reader","commentable":"false","commentCloseDate":"2015-09-09T14:00:09Z","standfirst":"<p>‘This dystopian thriller had me gripped from the beginning’</p>"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/2015/sep/09/red-queen-victoria-aveyard-review","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/childrens-books-site/2015/sep/09/red-queen-victoria-aveyard-review","sectionName":"Children's books","tags":[{"id":"childrens-books-site/childrens-books-site","webTitle":"Children's books","type":"blog","sectionId":"childrens-books-site","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/childrens-books-site","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/childrens-books-site/childrens-books-site","sectionName":"Children's books","references":[]},{"id":"books/booksforchildrenandteenagers","webTitle":"Children and teenagers","type":"keyword","sectionId":"books","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/books/booksforchildrenandteenagers","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/books/booksforchil