ng reviews about this book, I had high expectations. I’m very pleased to say that they were met! The way Aveyard weaved in so many twists and turns into the plot was supreme and despite only finishing this book a couple of days ago, I already want to read it again.</p> <p>The intricacy of the descriptions and situations give me an inkling that this will be a book that I will read many times and I will notice something slightly different. Even though I read the book with the attention that a predator gives its prey.</p> <p>This dystopian thriller had me gripped from the beginning. I think that this is a clever idea that has been perfectly executed - I can’t wait for the rest of the series!</p> <ul> <li><strong>Buy this book at the <a href=\"https://bookshop.theguardian.com/catalog/product/view/id/306435/\">Guardian Bookshop</a>.</strong><br /></li> </ul> <h2><strong>Want to tell the world about a book you’ve read? <a href=\"http://preview.gutools.co.uk/books/childrens-books/2011/mar/02/how-do-i-get-involved-guardian-childrens-books\">Join the site</a> and send us your review!</strong></h2>","productionOffice":"UK","hasStoryPackage":"false","trailText":"<strong>The Fanatical Reader: </strong>‘This dystopian thriller had me gripped from the beginning’","headline":"Red Queen by Victoria Aveyard – review","byline":"The Fanatical Reader","commentable":"false","commentCloseDate":"2015-09-09T14:00:09Z","standfirst":"<p>‘This dystopian thriller had me gripped from the beginning’</p>"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/2015/sep/09/red-queen-victoria-aveyard-review","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/childrens-books-site/2015/sep/09/red-queen-victoria-aveyard-review","sectionName":"Children's books","tags":[{"id":"childrens-books-site/childrens-books-site","webTitle":"Children's books","type":"blog","sectionId":"childrens-books-site","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/childrens-books-site/childrens-books-site","apiUrl":"http://content.guardiana