hor? </p> <p>It could be about growing up as one of seven children in Middleton, to a career that’s spanned everything from Spitting Image and The Day Today to Hollywood hits and <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/tv-and-radio/2013/aug/22/the-trip-boxset-review-steve-coogan\">The Trip</a>. </p> <p>So whether your favourite performance by Coogan was Alan Partridge, the Oscar-nominated <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/oct/31/philomena-review\">Philomena</a>, or as himself in front of the <a href=\"http://www.theguardian.com/media/2011/nov/22/leveson-inquiry-coogan-coulson-sting\">Leveson Inquiry</a> – now is your chance. Simply fill in the form below by 10pm on Sunday (13 September) and we will put the best ones to him.</p>  <figure class=\"element element-embed\" data-alt=\"steve coogan form\">  <iframe class=\"fenced\" srcdoc=\"&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;https://guardiannewsampampmedia.formstack.com/forms/js.php/untitled_form_19_copy_37&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;\"></iframe> </figure>","productionOffice":"UK","hasStoryPackage":"false","trailText":"Next week, we will be speaking to Steve Coogan ahead of his new autobiography, Easily Distracted, and we want to ask him your questions","headline":"Got a question for Steve Coogan? We want to hear it","commentable":"false","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441798732361/5869c27e-effb-433e-81a0-317d5af5cdad-140x84.jpeg","commentCloseDate":"2015-09-12T12:18:36Z","standfirst":"<p>Next week, we will be speaking to Steve Coogan ahead of his new autobiography, Easily Distracted, and we want to ask him your questions</p>"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/culture/2015/sep/09/got-a-question-for-steve-coogan-we-want-to-hear-it","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/culture/2015/sep/09/got-a-question-for-steve-coogan-we-want-to-hear-it","sectionName":"Culture","tag