y (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","mediaId":"dfd8efa4cb48cf73b19096d350755cdb8ee8293c","picdarUrn":"GD*24703219","width":"460"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799120609/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-540x324.jpeg","typeData":{"copyright":"Ronald Grant Archive","displayCredit":"true","secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799120609/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-540x324.jpeg","source":"PR","imageType":"Photograph","altText":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","suppliersReference":"LORD OF THE FLIES1963#2.JPG","height":"324","credit":"Photograph: PR","caption":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","mediaId":"dfd8efa4cb48cf73b19096d350755cdb8ee8293c","picdarUrn":"GD*24703219","width":"540"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799120829/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-140x84.jpeg","typeData":{"copyright":"Ronald Grant Archive","displayCredit":"true","secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799120829/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-140x84.jpeg","source":"PR","imageType":"Photograph","altText":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","suppliersReference":"LORD OF THE FLIES1963#2.JPG","height":"84","credit":"Photograph: PR","caption":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","mediaId":"dfd8efa4cb48cf73b19096d350755cdb8ee8293c","picdarUrn":"GD*24703219","width":"140"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799121026/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-1020x612.jpeg","typeData":{"copyright":"Ronald Grant Archive","displayCredit":"true","secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799121026/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-1020x612.jpeg","source":"PR","imageType":"Photograph","altText":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","suppliersReference":"LORD OF THE FLIES1963#2.JPG","height":"612","credit":"Photograph: PR","caption":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","mediaId":"dfd8efa4cb48cf73b19096d350755cdb8ee8293c","picdarUrn":"GD*24703219","width":"1020"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799121347/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-300x180.jpeg","typeData":{"copyright":"Ronald Grant Archive","displayCredit":"true","secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799121347/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-300x180.jpeg","source":"PR","imageType":"Photograph","altText":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","suppliersReference":"LORD OF THE FLIES1963#2.JPG","height":"180","credit":"Photograph: PR","caption":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","mediaId":"dfd8efa4cb48cf73b19096d350755cdb8ee8293c","picdarUrn":"GD*24703219","width":"300"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799121491/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-380x228.jpeg","typeData":{"copyright":"Ronald Grant Archive","displayCredit":"true","secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/9/9/1441799121491/4f55e3cb-2524-4dad-bc84-13216c461926-380x228.jpeg","source":"PR","imageType":"Photograph","altText":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","suppliersReference":"LORD OF THE FLIES1963#2.JPG","height":"228","credit":"Photograph: PR","caption":"Hugh Edwards as Piggy (right) in the 1963 film of Lord of the Flies","mediaId":"dfd8efa4cb48cf73b19096d350755cdb8ee8293c","picdarUrn":"GD*24703219","width":"380"}},{"type":"image","file":"ht